The following should be checked prior to release:

1.  Check build file(s) 
  - turn off test running (base.xml)
  - Set web.xml file to be non-ssl file (ir_web/build.xml)
  - Set yui to download and unzip (ir_web/build.xml)
  - Set zip version number (build.xml)
  
2.  Copy in help files
   - root of zip file
   - into web app pages/help
      (admin-help.pdf)
      (user-help.pdf)

3.  Copy ir_plus.properties file from test into production folder

4.  Ensure version is set in about page and build.xml

5.  Zip file

6.  Practice unzip and deployment on local machine - non-ssl based.